ilog.opl

Class IloOplDataElements

  • java.lang.Object
    • ilog.opl.IloOplDataSource
      • ilog.opl.IloOplDataElements

  • public class IloOplDataElements
extends IloOplDataSource
    Data elements used by an OPL model instance. An instance of this class represents the data used by an OPL model. It can be used as a data source for another model instance.
    See Also:
    IloOplModel
